205
00:16:40.291 --> 00:16:43.250
Betrayal's sting is sharp. isn't it?

206
00:16:43.916 --> 00:16:47.083
The Uroboros.
however. only tells the truth.

207
00:16:47.791 --> 00:16:50.583
He was the one who killed your mother.

208
00:16:51.833 --> 00:16:54.208
