to stop evil at its source.

230
00:18:08.833 --> 00:18:12.083
Every real.
God-fearing American loves him.

231
00:18:12.166 --> 00:18:13.958
We'll be hot this week. folks.

232
00:18:14.041 --> 00:18:17.916
